{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"readonly"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackProgress","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@MLNOfflinePackProgress","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgress"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The progress of an inactive or completed pack is computed lazily, and all its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"fields are set to 0 by default. To request the pack’s progress, use the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"-requestProgress","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method. To get notified when the progress becomes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"known and when it changes, observe KVO change notifications on this pack’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"state","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" key path. Alternatively, you can add an observer for","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification"},{"type":"text","text":"s about this pack that come from the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"default notification center."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/progress","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/progress"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The pack’s current progress."}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack(py)progress","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Property","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"progress","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"progress","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"}]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification":{"title":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackprogresschangednotification","abstract":[{"text":"Posted by the shared ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","type":"reference"},{"text":" object when an ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","type":"reference"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object’s progress changes. The progress may change due to a resource being","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"downloaded or because the pack discovers during the download that more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"resources are required for offline viewing. This notification is posted","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"whenever any field in the "},{"code":"progress","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property changes."}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"abstract":[{"text